---
const pains = [
  {
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12.76c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.087.16 2.185.283 3.293.369V21l4.076-4.076a1.526 1.526 0 0 1 1.037-.443 48.282 48.282 0 0 0 5.68-.494c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0 0 12 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018Z" />`,
    title: 'Reading and tagging every message',
    body: 'Every piece of feedback read manually, categorised by hand, and entered into a doc that\'s already out of date.',
  },
  {
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z" />`,
    title: 'Hunting for patterns and duplicates',
    body: 'Scrolling back through months of threads trying to spot what keeps coming up. No tool connects the dots automatically.',
  },
  {
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.182 15.182a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-6.364 0M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0ZM9.75 9.75c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75S9 10.164 9 9.75 9.168 9 9.375 9s.375.336.375.75Zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75Zm5.625 0c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75s-.375-.336-.375-.75.168-.75.375-.75.375.336.375.75Zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75Z" />`,
    title: 'Guessing at what actually matters',
    body: 'Without weighted signal, the loudest voice wins. Important accounts churn quietly while low-value noise fills the backlog.',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-center text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4">
      You're copying Slack threads into Notion. Pasting CSVs into spreadsheets. Arguing over whose customer is loudest.
    </p>
    <p class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium mb-12">Every week your PM is manually:</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {pains.map((pain) => (
        <div class="bg-[#0d1627] border border-[#1e2d4a] rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[#080e1a] border border-[#1e2d4a] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="#94a3b8" class="w-5 h-5">
              <Fragment set:html={pain.icon} />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">{pain.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">{pain.body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm mt-10">
      The result: slow decisions and missed revenue signals.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
